1.name: Microwave Oven
1.description: A microwave oven Sirius bought herself. Despite seeing heavy use, it somehow looks as pristine as the day it was purchased.

2.name: Coffee Machine
2.description: Sirius uses this to make coffee every morning.The machine still has traces of her fingerprints on it.

3.name: Mary Janes
3.description: The pair of shoes that Sirius wears all the time. They are loved and cared for, and thus the leather retains its soft luster.

4.name: Wall-Mounted Photograph
4.description: The subject is an orange tabby wearing a blue necktie. Behind the apparent sophistication lies a silly but cute appeal. It's safe to say the tenant likes this particular kind of cuteness.

5.name: Toaster
5.description: A very practical machine for the novice at-home cook. Drop in some bread slices, push down, and soon you'll have hot, crispy toast. You can of course adjust how toasty you want it.

6.name: Trash Can
6.description: Also known as a "rubbish bin" in some parts of the world. You look and you look, but you can't find anything unusual about this wholly unremarkable waste receptacle.

7.name: Blue Sky Picture Frame
7.description: This frame doesn't have a proper photo in it yet. The placeholder image is just there to look more appealing than a plain beige background.

8.name: Preserved Butterfly
8.description: The pattern on its wings reminds you of a wave washing up on a shore, and of Sirius sprinting across the sea, her hair fluttering in the wind. You should invite Sirius to go on a walk on the beach the next time you're free.

9.name: Floor Lamp
9.description: A floor lamp standing just by the couch. Sirius graciously thought ahead and picked a bulb that wouldn't strain your eyes. You could see yourself working from here every now and then.

10.name: Bread Plate
10.description: Two sandwiches and a croissant. Baked by Sirius, from the looks of it. Although they look and smell perfectly fine, you probably shouldn't taste them until Sirius urges you to.

11.name: Recreational Reading
11.description: A book lying on the table by the bed. Sirius has been reading this one quite a lot lately. After flipping through a few pages, you figure out that it's a story about a forbidden love between a maid and her master.

12.name: Wine Glasses
12.description: They're filled not with wine, but water. A perfect illustration of the kind of service Sirius provides. Although, drinking water from a wine glass with your pinky extended is a chore. You should tell her to get some regular glasses someday.

13.name: Legendary Sword Replica
13.description: A replica of the hero's sword from the smash hit port virtual reality RPG. The stand says, "For Kitchen Adventures." It's no wonder why the one in Sirius' room feels so much heavier.

14.name: Flower Arrangement 1
14.description: One of the fruits of Sirius' practicing of flower arrangement. While it isn't very varied in color, the flowers are distributed well. These would look better in a more open place.

15.name: Bedside Books
15.description: A pile of books lying by the bedside. Surprisingly, they're not all about cooking - they cover subjects like military tactics and how to provide optimal service. Sirius' personal notes are layered between the books. Judging by their contents, she's diligently studying to become an even better maid.

16.name: Dresser
16.description: Sirius must have been in a rush to see you, because she forgot to put the cap back on her lipstick. Be kind and do it for her!

17.name: Jewelry Case
17.description: An expensive piece of jewelry. Sirius hasn't worn it even once, preferring to keep it nice and safe behind the glass.

18.name: Flower Arrangement 2
18.description: A pair of pretty yellow roses. They bring a sunny mood to whatever table they find themselves atop. You start to wonder what flower is Sirius' favorite.

19.name: Mystery Novel
19.description: A mystery book yet to be even opened. One can assume this genre isn't Sirius' cup of tea for the time being.

20.name: Stuffed Shiba Inu
20.description: It has writing on its stomach that reads, "EXPERTLY CRAFTED BY AKASHI." Sirius is a regular patron of hers.

21.name: A Summer Memory
21.description: The float ring Sirius used when you went to the beach with her. It's placed in a very eye-catching location inside her home. Being a maid, she's hesitant to ask her master to go swimming with her for fear of making a faux pas. So instead, you should be the one to ask her.

22.name: Box of Books
22.description: A storage box for regular workbooks. Sirius says the notepads outline her maidly work schedules. You see half-faded writing on the label on the cover. "The Ways I Want to Be --------" it says - half of the title has been almost completely erased.

23.name: Watering Pot
23.description: A watering can keeps the potted plants and flowers around the room happy. This is not a watering can. It's very blatantly a teapot. You wonder what bizarre thinking led Sirius to start using this in place of a proper watering can.

24.name: Nightlight
24.description: A nightlight with an endearing design.Sirius got it so she wouldn't trip and fall when she gets up at night.Its warm light reminds you of the warmth of her smile.

25.name: Sunglasses
25.description: The pair of sunglasses Sirius brought with her to the beach.She leaves them where they're always in reach.

26.name: Body Lotion
26.description: Sirius uses this body lotion after her baths.Sometimes, you can smell its faint aroma even from the door to her quarters.

27.name: Aroma Diffuser
27.description: This diffuser exudes a mild floral scent. Sirius chose it with great care.The aroma supposedly relieves stress and helps the mind relax.

28.name: White Towel
28.description: This white towel was haphazardly left here. It's still slightly moist to the touch.Maybe Sirius just got done in the bathroom? Who knows.

29.name: How to Win Your Commander's Heart - Volume 2
29.description: A book Sirius left by her bedside.What is this book doing here?Also, they made TWO volumes of this?

30.name: Half-Drunk Milk
30.description: Half full, or half empty? Either way, it's sitting on the table and has faint lip markings along its rim.

31.name: Splendid Sandcastle
31.description: This sandcastle shines golden under the sun. Its builder put clear effort into everything down to the smallest details.You can readily picture just how much work was put into it.Here's hoping that the waves won't wash it away.

32.name: Beach Tools
32.description: A shovel and a bucket lying in the sand. Looks like someone was using them until just a minute ago.You think to yourself that maybe you should have a sandcastle-building contest next time you visit the beach with someone.

33.name: Seabreeze Guitar
33.description: A wooden guitar, forgotten and left behind by its own. Brine lingers inside its cavity, and it smells like the sea. Its notes sound almost like the lapping of waves on a beach.

34.name: Half-Consumed Drink
34.description: A partially drunk beverage. It's still cold, with drops of condensation gently running down its sides. Whoever this belonged to earlier, the beached has claimed it now.

35.name: Surfboards
35.description: These surfboards have been casually left here. Their many scratches whisper stories about past encounters with fierce waves. Maybe you should go surfing the next time you visit the beach with someone.

36.name: Cooler
36.description: A cute little cooler. Someone must have packed for some sort of party, because it's stuffed full of drinks and snacks. You can't help but wonder where its owner has gone.

37.name: Inner Tubes
37.description: Two inner tubes, one in blue and one in yellow, silently resting on the beach. While they look pretty old, they are still able to do their job perfectly well.

38.name: Trash Can
38.description: A trash can with a humble design. Remember: don't litter on the beach! Keeping it clean is just as important as keeping the oceans clean.

39.name: Lantern
39.description: A lantern with a simple design. When it gets dark at the beach, this can be a real lifesaver. It's all but begging to be brought along on a fantastical nightly stroll along the sea.

51.name: Hanami Dango Plate
51.description:
The delectable dango rest quietly on a ceramic plate,
perfectly complementing the tablecloth's design.
Enjoy them with her later.

52.name: Tri-Color Mochi

53.name: Opened Book
53.description:
A book on traditional Sakuran tea ceremonies,
its corners slightly weathered.
Noshiro appears to revisit this book often,
leaving many neat notes on the last pages.

54.name: Bedding
54.description:
Neatly folded bedding.
The precise corners are a testament to its owner's diligence.

55.name: Uniform
55.description:
The uniform hanging on the wall is the same as the one she is wearing.
Looks like this is the outfit she likes the most.

56.name: Sakuran Sweets
56.description:
A beautifully arranged assortment of Sakuran sweets, each handmade by Noshiro.
Though they may almost be too pretty to eat,
be sure to savor them later - lest her hard work will go to waste!

57.name: Wind Chime
57.description:
A wind chime hangs by the window,
producing a clear melody as the breeze passes through.
According to Noshiro, it's one of the best ways to beat the summer heat.

58.name: Wind Chime 2
58.description:
This wind chime produces a deeper tone than the glass one.
Noshiro has purposefully hung it up elsewhereso the different notes interweave, creating a unique mood.

59.name: Shopping Bag
59.description:
A paper bag bearing a coffee shop logo.
Noshiro treats it with great care,
more than you'd expect for a regular paper bag.

60.name: Sakuran Kimono
60.description:
The gold-thread embroidery on this kimono's sleeves speaks of its elegance.
It's Noshiro's favorite.
She always conducts herself carefully when she wears it outside.

61.name: Preserved Flowers
61.description:
Yellow roses carefully preserved inside a bell jar.
The petals retain their vivid color even to this day.

62.name: Pine Bonsai
62.description:
A small pine tree bonsai.
The branches have been trimmed in a plain yet tasteful way.
Noshiro tends to it daily, preserving its natural beauty in perfect form.

63.name: Water Ornament
63.description:
A Sakuran ornament that typically goes in the garden but, in this case, has been placed in a corner of the room.
When water flows in, it produces a clear and pleasant sound.

64.name: Sakuran Umbrella
64.description:
This folded umbrella rests against the wall.
Noshiro often carries it with her when she goes outside.
When it's raining, obviously.

65.name: Round Cushion
65.description:
A round cushion in a bright color.
While it looks firm at a glance, it's surprisingly comfy to sit on.
Maybe you should put one in your office too?

66.name: Sushi Platter
66.description:
A tray lined with hand-formed sushi and other delicacies.
Every item is meticulously placed,
and even the decorative elements are well-thought-out.
Surprisingly, sushi rolls are even included.
Turns out Noshiro isn't a stickler for tradition.

67.name: Cherry Blossom Branch
67.description:
A cherry blossom branch left on the table.
The pink petals almost glow on the branch, lending a touch of spring mood.

68.name: Stack of Books
68.description:
A stack of books piled atop one another.
The subjects covered range from tea ceremonies to flower arrangement and traditional etiquette.
Based on where the bookmark is, Noshiro is studying a new flower arrangement technique.

70.name: Kettle
70.description:
An unremarkable kettle.
Noshiro often uses it when making tea.
Despite its signs of heavy use, it's still in good condition thanks to diligent care.

71.name: Stone Lantern
71.description:
A lantern made of stone, inspired by traditional Sakuran garden lanterns.
It lends an air of tranquility to wherever it's placed.

72.name: Tied Hanging Scrolls
72.description:
These scrolls rest quietly in the corner of the study,
their knots perfectly tied.
Though not unfurled, they still convey Noshiro's meticulous care.

74.name: Wooden Lantern
74.description:
A square, wooden lantern that's been placed in a corner.
A soft light glows through the translucent paper.
Noshiro picked this furnishing after careful deliberation.

75.name: Floor Lamp
75.description:
An austere Sakuran-style floor lamp. It glows with a soft light.
Beneath its shade hangs a delicate wind chime ornament.
It creates a quiet, serene space where you can spend a peaceful time with Noshiro.

76.name: Humidifier
76.description:
This white humidifier operates silently most of the time,
only sometimes making a faint hum.
Noshiro placed it in a corner where it can slowly release moist air.
She says it's good for her skin.

77.name: Skincare Oil
77.description:
The oil inside the bottle emits a delicate fragrance.
According to Noshiro, it's extracted from camellias.
It's one of her favorite skincare products.

78.name: Perfume Bottle
78.description:
A bottle of perfume with a simple design.
Light softly reflects off its glass surface.
Upon closer inspection, you notice that this is the very bottle you gifted her.

79.name: Reed Diffuser
79.description:
A diffuser with a delicate fragrance.
Its subtle aroma fills the room.
It's the scent that always lingers around Noshiro.

101.name: Balloons and Photo
101.description:
A framed photo decorated with carefully selected balloons.
Anchorage loves this little combo.
The bunny bow is still crinkled from the last time she tied it.

102.name: Bunny Tea Set
102.description:
A bunny-themed teapot and tiny cups to match.
Anchorage takes good care of them.

103.name: Wish List
103.description:
A chalkboard hanging on the wall.
Anchorage often writes her little goals on it.
Sometimes, you can see cute little doodles.

104.name: Trove of Knowledge
104.description:
Fairy tale books are neatly arranged in the bookcase.
All of them are wrapped, labeled, and sorted 
under Anchorage's personal system.

105.name: Castle Storage
105.description:
A file storage container modeled after a fairy-tale castle.
Anchorage uses it to store various notes and important documents.

106.name: Classic Piano
106.description:
A classic piano in the corner of the room.
The last score that Anchorage was learning is open on it, 
with careful notes taken here and there.

107.name: Crayon Drawing
107.description:
Some crayon art left on Anchorage's desk.
It depicts the most beautiful thing she's ever seen, 
which seems to be... the Commander?

108.name: Alarm Clock
108.description:
An alarm clock with a traditional, if not plain, design.
It sits on Anchorage's nightstand, 
ensuring that she never misses an important moment.

109.name: Storage Box
109.description:
A storage box with a cute design.
Anchorage keeps all kinds of odds and ends inside.

110.name: Floatie
110.description:
A swim ring adorned with stars.
Anchorage considers it a summer must-have.

111.name: Safety Knife
111.description:
A beginner's kitchen knife that won't cut through skin.
Anchorage has been learning how to cut veggies, 
no doubt dreaming of making delicious dishes someday.

112.name: Fairy Tale Picture Book
112.description:
A hardcover picture book.
Anchorage keeps it safely stored, 
though you can see the traces of her rapt reading on the pages.

113.name: Fluffy Plushie
113.description:
A penguin plushie wearing a little nightcap.
Anchorage gives it pride of place on the sofa, 
perhaps hoping that the penguin will watch over her as she dreams.

114.name: Cactus
114.description:
An adorable cactus.
Anchorage has given it a colorful pot, 
adding some warmth to its life.

115.name: Kitchenware
115.description:
A kitchenware set for playing house.
Anchorage has arranged them neatly on the wall.
It's a little early for her to start cooking for real...

116.name: Orca Chair
116.description:
A rocking chair made to look like a killer whale.
It's one of Anchorage's favorite places.

117.name: Basket
117.description:
A storage basket woven with rattan.
Anchorage keeps her daily necessities in it.

118.name: Whale Plushie
118.description:
A blue whale plushie with round eyes and a friendly smile.
She must like collecting plushies.
Why not bring her a few some time?

119.name: Small Blackboard
119.description:
On the blackboard is Anchorage's cute handwriting.
But what is this equation supposed to mean, exactly...?

120.name: Cube Cushion
120.description:
A light-blue cushion in the shape of a die.
One side features a cute manta ray, 
and its soft colors add a hint of peace to the room.

121.name: Adorned Photos
121.description:
Rope and wooden clips hold up various beloved photos.
Each of them is filled with warm memories of Anchorage.

122.name: Umbrella Stand
122.description:
A simple umbrella stand.
Anchorage diligently stores her umbrellas inside, 
ready for a rainy day.

123.name: Thermos
123.description:
A brightly-colored thermos bottle.
When it's cold out, Anchorage puts a hot drink inside.

124.name: Stickers
124.description:
One sticker is a star, and the other is a manjuu.
They're put up in an inconspicuous place, 
but it adds life to the room.

125.name: Bedside Lamp
125.description:
A delicate bedside lamp.
Anchorage sets it at the softest setting before bed, 
letting the warm light lull her into sweet dreams.

126.name: Whale Pendant Light
126.description:
A huge ceiling lamp shaped like a humpback whale.
Anchorage gazes up at it from her bed, 
imagining herself deep in a dreamy underwater world.

127.name: Manjuu Mug
127.description:
A mug that looks like a manjuu.
Anchorage's love for it is evident from 
how she places it in the most conspicuous spot.

128.name: Bath Towels
128.description:
Perfectly folded bath towels.
They look like little clouds drifting across the sky together.

1101.name: Caramel Popcorn
1101.description:
Freshly microwaved popcorn covered in amber caramel coating.
It's a must-have for any movies watched in New Jersey's home.

1102.name: Bunny Apron
1102.description:
An apron hung up in the corner of the kitchen.
It has a simple yet cute rabbit graphic on the front.
She's always full of energy, even when cooking and cleaning.

1103.name: Juicer
1103.description:
One powerful juicer.
Every morning, she throws all kinds of fruits into it,
and out comes a colorful and refreshing juice.

1104.name: Bowl of Strawberries
1104.description:
Fresh, plump strawberries fill the bowl,
each one glistening with beads of water.
Her fingers reach for one,
and you find your heart skipping a beat as she places it in her mouth.

1105.name: Range Hood
1105.description:
Every kitchen needs a range hood.
That familiar humming is proof that
the Big J is showing off her cooking skills!

1106.name: Lemon Water
1106.description:
A pitcher full of cool, refreshing lemon water.
It's the perfect balance of sour and sweet,
with a few sugar cubes dissolved within.

1107.name: White Jacket
1107.description:
New Jersey's everyday wear, a light but stylish jacket.
She took off the jacket and threw it onto a chair -
the very first thing she does when she gets home.

1108.name: Toaster
1108.description:
A toaster with an adorable design.
Press down the lever, and crispy golden toast will pop out.
Add some jam, honey, or butter for the perfect breakfast!

1109.name: Jungle Vibes
1109.description:
A potted sansevieria plant growing steadily.
It quietly spreads its leaves in the corner of the room.
With every breath,
you can feel the fresh, revitalizing air it brings.

1110.name: Glazed Donut
1110.description:
New Jersey made this for afternoon tea.
"Gotta taste-test before I let you eat it, honey!" she says,
licking the sugar off of her lips.

1111.name: Robot Vacuum
1111.description:
A cute cleaning robot that leaves your room spick and span.
It dutifully gathers not just dust, but the traces of everyday life as well.

1112.name: 4K TV
1112.description:
When the 55-inch screen lights up,
it becomes a door to worlds unknown.
What will it be today?
Explosive action? Or a kiss in the rain on Union streets?

1113.name: Fashion Magazines
1113.description:
Magazines that have been read over and over are piled on the table.
This is her fashion supply station, an endless fount of inspiration.

1114.name: Handbag
1114.description:
A nice handbag left lazily on the floor.
It's filled with all sorts of useful little things.
No doubt she took it on countless adventures again today.

1115.name: Sports Gear
1115.description:
A whole set of exercise clothes and items.
The ever-energetic New Jersey is always ready for a serious aerobic workout!

1116.name: Big J Nameplate
1116.description:
A dragon lurks within! No coming in without permission!
"...Hm? Honey, you're here?! Come in, come in!"

1117.name: Clothes Rack
1117.description:
When she's picking out clothes for a date,
all of them seem to scream, "Pick me!"
That supposedly simple "What to wear?" question?
Not so simple when it really counts.

1118.name: Clear Tote
1118.description:
A tote filled with cosmetics and the like.
These are must-have items for daily commuting and travel,
so she can redo her makeup any time!

1119.name: Bunny Ears
1119.description:
A quirky bunny hood with ears that move according to your mood.
This is one of Big J's favorite accessories.

1120.name: Air Conditioner
1120.description:
Among the greatest human inventions in history.
It adjusts the room temperature to exactly what you need,
creating a soothing space for ultimate relaxation.

1121.name: Air Purifier
1121.description:
A quiet air purifier stands in the corner.
Its unceasing, reliable operation makes every breath a luxurious one.

1122.name: Frozen Drinks
1122.description:
Two frozen drinks radiating icy coolness.
Whether you drink alone or with someone you love,
every sip is the very picture of bliss.

1123.name: Wireless Speaker
1123.description:
A portable, stylish speaker packed with melodies ranging from classical to rock.
The right tune always awaits you.

1124.name: Bunny Nightlight
1124.description:
An adorable nightlight that looks like a bunny.
It casts a soft blue glow, illuminating the way in the darkness.

1125.name: Dumbbells
1125.description:
A pair of dumbbells, just the right weight,
perfectly suited to New Jersey's workout needs.
With every drop of sweat,
she finds a better version of herself than the day before.

1126.name: Curling Iron
1126.description:
A curling iron with a sleek design, the perfect helper for hair styling.
Be sure to unplug it after use!

1127.name: Black Stockings
1127.description:
In her room, every stocking seems to have the travel bug.
That's seven and a half pairs vanished this month alone.

1128.name: Skincare Set
1128.description:
A comprehensive set of skincare products, New Jersey's personal beauty lab.
Sometimes the oddest combinations yield the most surprising results.

1201.name: Porcelain
1201.description: White porcelain with intricate patterns on display. It's pristine and shiny, proving how well Taihou cares for it.

1202.name: After-School Fun
1202.description: A uniform with an armband and a skirt. It's a nice change of style from her usual red dress.

1203.name: Forbidden Feast
1203.description: An elegant red slip dress made of soft, light fabric. Taihou wears it to parties and other special occasions.

1204.name: Wooden Storage Box
1204.description: A box containing her treasure collection. It's full of memories of her beloved.

1205.name: Small Bonsai
1205.description: A beautifully maintained bonsai with glossy and vibrant leaves. You can tell at a glance how much care it's given.

1206.name: Phoenix Hairpin
1206.description: A hair ornament with a phoenix motif is left on her vanity. It's the same as the one she always wears. She clearly likes it enough to have multiple.

1207.name: Geta Clogs
1207.description: A pair of traditional geta, with patterns carved into their wooden soles. When worn on a stroll, they make one's footsteps all the more musical.

1208.name: Book Collection
1208.description: Subjects in her collection range from literature to military affairs. Some of these books also seem a little... odd?

1209.name: Incense Burner
1209.description: The incense burner emits a floral scent. Before bedtime, she likes to fill her room with tranquil aromas.

1210.name: Cat Tree
1210.description: A cat tree with a cute design, complete with a toy ball on top. Is she thinking of getting a cat, maybe?

1211.name: Aromatherapy Candle
1211.description: The candle serves as both illumination and decoration. Taihou has also mixed in some essential oils, adding a gentle lavender scent when it burns.

1212.name: Vivacious Flowers
1212.description: A vibrant arrangement of brightly colored flowers sits by the window. Taihou regularly takes care of the collection, maintaining its freshness.

1213.name: Cat Bowls
1213.description: Brand-new cat bowls divided by color - white for water, black for food.

1214.name: Fruit Bowl
1214.description: A bowl of fresh, delicious-looking fruit sits on the table. She always keeps it filled for her guests' convenience.

1215.name: Full-Size Fridge
1215.description: A large refrigerator full of fruit, vegetables, sweets, and drinks. Taihou frequently replaces the contents to suit her whims.

1216.name: Ceramic Knife
1216.description: A high-quality ceramic kitchen knife. Taihou never fails to use it when making heartfelt lunches for a certain someone.

1217.name: Kettle
1217.description: She often uses this kettle to make tea. Apparently, she accidentally burned herself a lot when she first started.

1218.name: Temari Ball
1218.description: An exquisite temari ball, but it looks like it's only for decoration. She probably hasn't played with it in a long time - you could ask her to teach you how to play.

1219.name: Cushioned Seat
1219.description: A dark, round cushion. It's comfortable, but so low that it's clearly meant to be used on a tatami floor.

1220.name: Tuna Sushi
1220.description: Fresh sushi with fatty tuna. It's part of a special meal set aside for a loved one. She has more kinds on offer, too.

1221.name: Loving Lunch
1221.description: A luxurious bento box with nine compartments. The selection of foods is diverse, creating an effective nutritional balance and flavors that you'll never forget.

1222.name: Wooden Cabinet
1222.description: This small wooden cabinet by the entrance neatly displays her various odds and ends.

1223.name: Kitchen Set
1223.description: A tool set comprising a frying pan, ladle, spatula, and more. All of them are clean and hang neatly on the wall.

1224.name: Paper Fan
1224.description: A traditional red Sakuran fan, illustrated with wild geese and white cherry blossoms. Taihou made it herself.

1225.name: Calligraphy Desk
1225.description: A simple desk with calligraphy paper on top. Sometimes, she writes or paints here.

1226.name: Decorative Flowers
1226.description: A display of flowers with subtle colors and a pleasingly uneven arrangement.

1227.name: Range Hood
1227.description: A practical, efficient, and quiet range hood is placed over the stove.

1228.name: Framed Fan
1228.description: A fan is placed in a frame for decoration. It hangs in a conspicuous place, immediately catching the eye.

1229.name: Kitty Wall Scroll
1229.description: A piece of cat artwork is prominently displayed. The confident brush strokes give a glimpse of the artist's love for cats.

1230.name: Ceramic Cups
1230.description: A collection of exquisite ceramic cups with fancy patterns. Their smooth surfaces are inviting and pleasant to the touch.

1601.name: Menu
1601.description:
The variety of drinks on this menu helps you see what this caf is all about at a glance.
Each cup is full of creativity and care, satisfying even the most unique tastes.

1602.name: Signs
1602.description: Convenient signs guide you to the coziest corners of the caf. First impressions matter!

1603.name: Candle
1603.description: Warm, gentle light cultivates a romantic and relaxing vibe.

1604.name: Order Counter
1604.description: The monitor is operated by touch screen, and its design is simple yet functional. Ordering and payment are quick and easy.

1605.name: Bottle
1605.description: The bottle is designed by an expert craftsman. Its appearance and practicality make your morning cup of coffee more refined and enjoyable.

1606.name: Chocolate Donut
1606.description:
Crispy on the outside, tender on the inside. A classic, delicious dessert.
Every bite leaves a lasting impression of joy on your taste buds.

1607.name: Cocktail Set
1607.description: Cocktails mixed with professional tools make the night much more colorful.

1608.name: Napkins
1608.description: Soft, clean napkins lie ready to attend to any and all cleaning needs.

1609.name: Carved Mascot
1609.description: A carving of the caf's iconic mascot.
